    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title">&#x201C;First Sketch of &#x2018;Andernach&#x2019;&#x201D;<ref type="gloss" target="andernacht_poem_glosses_textual.php#ANDERNACHTVERSIONGLOSS"/></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>W<hi rend="smallcaps">e</hi> have wound a weary way;</l>
                    <l>Twilight&#x02BC;s mists are gathering grey.</l>
                    <l>Purple now the hills are showing;</l>
                    <l>Bright the western clouds are glowing.</l>
                    <l>Lashing on with giant force,</l>
                    <l>Rolls the <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> his sullen course;</l>
                    <l>Flash his waves with flamy red,</l>
                    <l>Eddying o&#x02BC;er their <name type="geological" corresp="#BASALT">basalt</name> bed;&#x2014;</l>
                    <l>Now with wide expanded breast,</l>
                    <l>Now between the hills compressed;</l>
                    <l>Ever noble, ever free,</l>
                    <l>Flows his river majesty.</l>
                    <l>Now upon the evening skies</l>
                    <l><placeName corresp="#ANDERNACH">Andernacht</placeName>&#x20BC;s grey ruins rise,&#x2014;<ref type="gloss" target="andernacht_glosses_contextual.php#ANDERNACHTSGREYRUINSGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Memorials of the Roman power;&#x2014;<ref type="gloss" target="andernacht_glosses_contextual.php#ROMANPOWERGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Buttress and battlement and tower,</l>
                    <l>Decaying, falling fast away,</l>
                    <l>The monuments of C&#x00E6;sar&#x02BC;s sway,&#x2014;</l>
                    <l>In heaps together loosely thrown,&#x2014;</l>
                    <l>The sculptured head, inscriptioned stone:</l>
                    <l>Unguarded now the bridge&#x02BC;s length,</l>
                    <l>And failing fast its arches&#x02BC; strength;</l>
                    <l>The green sod in the moat is growing,</l>
                    <l>The cold wind in the chambers blowing,</l>
                    <l>And, flapping through the thin night air,</l>
                    <l>The owl and bat, the tenants there.</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
